{"article_id":"S0kB0T4j1uop8XlC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"San Juan Mayor Carmen Yulin Cruz told President Trump Tuesday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that hurricane relief efforts in Puerto Rico were `` not about politics , ''","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"just days after Trump sparred with Cruz over the federal government 's response to the island .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Interested in Donald Trump ?","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Add Donald Trump as an interest","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest Donald Trump news , video , and analysis from .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Add Interest","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"`` It ' s all about saving lives ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"it ' s not about politics , ''","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Cruz said to Trump","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"as they shook hands","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"following a briefing earlier in the day .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Trump accused Cruz of \" poor leadership \"","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and speculated","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"that `` Democrats '' told her to `` be nasty to Trump '' in a barrage of tweets over the weekend","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"after the mayor decried a comment by the Acting Homeland Security Secretary Elaine Duke ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"who said","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"she thought","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"the federal government 's actions in Puerto Rico were `` a good news story .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"'' ... Such poor leadership ability by the Mayor of San Juan , and others in Puerto Rico ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"who are not able to get their workers to help .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"They ....","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"September 30 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"It was originally unclear if Trump and Cruz would meet ,","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"but on Tuesday morning Cruz announced","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that she had been invited to the briefing","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and had accepted the invite .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"`` I will use this opportunity","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"to reiterate the primary message :","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"This is about saving lives , not about politics ;","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"this is also about giving the people of Puerto Rico the respect","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"we deserve ;","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"and recognizing the moral imperative","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"to do both , ''","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Cruz said in a statement prior to the meeting .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"Trump touted the response to Hurricane Maria","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"as he attended the briefing on relief efforts ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"that the territory 's officials `` can be proud '' of the relatively low death toll on the island","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"compared to Hurricane Katrina in 2005 .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Noting","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"that `` every death is a horror , ''","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Trump called Katrina `` a real catastrophe ''","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"given its `` hundreds and hundreds and hundreds of people","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"that died , ''","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"before asking a Puerto Rican official for their `` death count . ''","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"`` Sixteen people certified , ''","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Trump noted .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"`` Sixteen people versus in the thousands .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"You can be very proud of all of your people and all of our people","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"working together .","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"Sixteen versus literally thousands of people .","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"You can be very proud . ''","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"After the president left San Juan ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Puerto Rico Gov . Ricardo Rossello announced","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"the death toll from Maria rose to 34 .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Cruz characterized the president as having a `` lack of sensibility '' in an interview with CNN Tuesday afternoon .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"She later told the network","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that she felt","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"the most productive part of the meeting was when she met with White House staffers .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"`` I truly believe","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"that they finally saw the connection , or the disconnect , between what they were hearing on the one hand and the reality","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"of what is happening on the ground , ''","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"the mayor said .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"But Cruz denounced Trump 's visit as a public relations stunt","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and criticized how he handed out supplies at Calvary Chapel .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"`` His terrible and abominable view","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"of him","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"throwing paper towels","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"and throwing provisions at people ,","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"it 's really --","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"it does not embody the spirit of the American nation , ''","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"Cruz said in an interview with MSNBC Tuesday night .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Pres . Trump tosses rolls of paper towels","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"to crowd in Puerto Rico amid visit","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"to survey damage from Hurricane Maria","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"https : //t.co/OBh60B2jro","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"pic.twitter.com/FZLgcGOiIi","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"- Politics","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"( @ ABCPolitics )","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"October 3 , 2017","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Trump told reporters aboard Air Force One","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"that he heard zero criticism during the visit","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"and described the day as `` terrific '' and `` great . ''","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"`` They were so thankful for what we ' ve done , \"","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"\" We only heard 'thank yous ' from the people of Puerto Rico ...","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"I enjoyed very much being with them . \"","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"Hurricane Maria carved a path of destruction across Puerto Rico two weeks ago in a storm season","depth":4},{"id":91,"text":"that has already seen hurricanes Harvey and Irma create billions of dollars in damage in Texas , Louisiana and Florida .","depth":4},{"id":92,"text":"Trump said Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"it would be costly to rebuild the island","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"and restore its infrastructure","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"following the storm .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"`` I hate to tell you , Puerto Rico ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"but you 've thrown our budget a little out of whack , ''","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"said Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"`` because we 've spent a lot of money on Puerto Rico","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"and that 's fine .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"We saved a lot of lives . ''","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"The president has repeatedly defended the federal response to Puerto Rico","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"despite facing severe criticism .","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"\" It ' s been amazing what ' s been done in a very short period of time on Puerto Rico , \"","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"the president said in the Oval Office Monday .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"The island is still grappling with the damage","depth":4},{"id":107,"text":"caused by Hurricane Maria .","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"Only 47 percent of the island ' s water customers have access to potable water","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"and 95 percent of Puerto Rico is still without power ,","depth":5},{"id":110,"tex